  "prompt": "What's the creepiest thing your pet has ever done?",
  "response": "While I don't have personal experiences or pets, I can share some common creepy stories pet owners often describe. For instance, many people report their pets staring at seemingly nothing, especially at night, which can be unsettling. Some have experienced their pets suddenly bolting out of nowhere or standing at a door and barking when no one is there. Others have had pets make unusual noises, like eerie howls or growls, at odd hours. Each of these moments can leave owners feeling a little on edge! Do you have a pet with any creepy habits?",
